 `/home/clashuser/hzh/work_bo/codex_manager/vscode-extension`. Next handoff stays narrow: surface when the dashboard is showing cached/persisted insights data.\"}}\n.codex-loop/state/logs/tick_20260416_044051_last_message.txt:1:Completed one bounded mailbox analysis loop.\n.codex-loop/state/logs/tick_20260416_044051_last_message.txt:3:Audited the agent recovery filter in [src/host/team-coordination.js](/home/clashuser/hzh/work_bo/codex_manager/vscode-extension/recovered/codex-managed-agent-0.0.71/extension/src/host/team-coordination.js:250). The probe verified valid agent files recover, mismatched and unsafe agent files are ignored, valid task recovery still works, and event/inbox ID behavior did not drift. `node --check src/host/team-coordination.js` passed. No code changed in this pass, so packaging was not required.\n.codex-loop/state/logs/tick_20260416_044051_last_message.txt:5:The analysis found one containment risk: [ensureAgentRecord](/home/clashuser/hzh/work_bo/codex_manager/vscode-extension/recovered/codex-managed-agent-0.0.71/extension/src/host/team-coordination.js:206) can preserve and rewrite a mismatched existing `agent_id` envelope. Updated [ACTIVE_PLAN.md](/home/clashuser/hzh/work_bo/codex_manager/vscode-extension/recovered/codex-managed-agent-0.0.71/extension/.claude/plans/ACTIVE_PLAN.md:19) and wrote [evolution-2026-04-16-mailbox-agent-recovery-filter-analysis.md](/home/clashuser/hzh/work_bo/codex_manager/vscode-extension/recovered/codex-managed-agent-0.0.71/extension/.claude/plans/loloop/evolution-2026-04-16-mailbox-agent-recovery-filter-analysis.md:1). Synced both plan files to `/home/clashuser/hzh/work_bo/codex_manager/vscode-extension` and verified with `cmp`.\n.codex-loop/state/logs/tick_20260416_044051_last_message.txt:7:Next smallest handoff: execute only the `ensureAgentRecord` hardening slice in `.claude/plans/ACTIVE_PLAN.md`, making the computed filename-safe `nextAgentId` authoritative over any existing or patch-provided `agent_id`, witho