ck_20260414_121459_last_message.txt:3:审计结论是：当前 unified board 的主要问题不是 action dispatch。`attach`、`pin`、`Codex`、`auto loop` 这些动作已经按 thread identity 和 thread `cwd` 执行，路径无关性基本成立；真正的最小缺口在 board card 的 path-awareness 还不够紧凑，卡片副标题仍然依赖原始 `cwd` 文本，见 [src/webview-template.js](/home/clashuser/export/codex-managed-agent/src/webview-template.js#L5413) 和 [src/host/auto-continue.js](/home/clashuser/export/codex-managed-agent/src/host/auto-continue.js#L251)。所以这轮把下一 slice 收敛成一个更小、更直接的 UI parity 修复：只给 board cards 补一个 compact root-identity cue。\n.codex-loop/state/logs/tick_20260414_121459_last_message.txt:7:下一轮 handoff 保持同一轨道且不扩张：只在 unified board 的 card surface 上补一个 compact root-identity cue，减少对 raw `cwd` subtitle 的依赖，不进入 toolbar filtering、board regrouping 或更大的 cross-path redesign。\n.codex-loop/state/logs/tick_20260414_095014.log:87:{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_2\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc \\\"sed -n '52,92p' .claude/plans/active-codex-managed-agent-roadmap.md\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"### Milestone 3 — Insight and Guidance Layer\\nStatus: active\\n\\nTargets:\\n- stabilize usage report generation\\n- improve topic map / word cloud / weekly shift interaction\\n- make guidance more actionable and durable\\n\\nAudit findings:\\n- host-side insights fallback already reads a persisted usage report from `~/.codex/codex_managed_agent_usage_report.json`\\n- webview UI state persists topic-driven navigation state through `vscode.setState()`\\n- first bounded reliability gap: persisted `topicFocus` is not revalidated against current insights data or current threads after reload\\n- host-side persisted-report fallback is sufficient for webview reload recovery; a second reload-survivable webview cache would be redundant right now\\n\\nCompleted in this milestone:\\n- persisted `topicFocus` is now cleared on reload when current thread data no longer supports the saved insight navigation state\\n- active-session insights rendering now reus