lter-analysis.md](/home/clashuser/hzh/work_bo/codex_manager/vscode-extension/recovered/codex-managed-agent-0.0.71/extension/.claude/plans/loloop/evolution-2026-04-16-mailbox-agent-recovery-filter-analysis.md:1). Synced both plan files to `/home/clashuser/hzh/work_bo/codex_manager/vscode-extension` and verified with `cmp`.\\n\\nNext smallest handoff: execute only the `ensureAgentRecord` hardening slice in `.claude/plans/ACTIVE_PLAN.md`, making the computed filename-safe `nextAgentId` authoritative over any existing or patch-provided `agent_id`, without changing agent file paths, task creation, IDs, UI, stale recovery, or board/tab semantics.\"}}\n.codex-loop/state/logs/tick_20260416_042007.log:60:{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_0\",\"type\":\"agent_message\",\"text\":\"Using `codex-loop` for the required analysis pass. I’ll read the plan files in order, audit the `appendEvent` guard, and then set the next bounded mailbox hardening target.\"}}\n.codex-loop/state/logs/tick_20260416_042007.log:95:      <div class=\"data\"><div class=\"main-wrapper\" role=\"main\"><div class=\"main-content\"><noscript><div class=\"h2\"><span id=\"challenge-error-text\">Enable JavaScript and cookies to continue</span></div></noscript></div></div><script>(function(){window._cf_chl_opt = {cFPWv: 'g',cH: 'bqDIoyQejOQRRKtSwX2KwccW7sKg7Ge0sUo4dkdYG5g-1776313223-1.2.1.1-w0ixqlMafGLrCl6u9_bYXDx2mpG.V.I0js6x.uvtn4glkiCxZHq5DhU4WY_t8C8L',cITimeS: '1776313223',cRay: '9ed065b1ae8f3f37',cTplB: '0',cTplC:1,cTplO:0,cTplV:5,cType: 'managed',cUPMDTk:\"/backend-api/codex/analytics-events/events?__cf_chl_tk=U3.7R6VTN7Vi69qoG1kzuFXahbyWRedXHAQkF0NBVkk-1776313223-1.0.1.1-_zHNktv2.yuH8PFNhR_2WA5_FZiWCxfolOH3IhdYumA\",cvId: '3',cZone: 'chatgpt.com',fa:\"/backend-api/codex/analytics-events/events?__cf_chl_f_tk=U3.7R6VTN7Vi69qoG1kzuFXahbyWRedXHAQkF0NBVkk-1776313223-1.0.1.1-_zHNktv2.yuH8PFNhR_2WA5_FZiWCxfolOH3IhdYumA\",md: '6Hx1tKSMIcvx6RYTRWYKBxJ4EYhxv6K.Q1eVH446EmI-1776313223-1.2.1.1-j56JAk